    "date": "2021-02-23T16:06:35Z",
    "text": "Academic Research Protection Act\n\nThis bill directs certain federal agencies to take specified steps to protect federally funded academic research from foreign threats, establishes the National Commission on Academic Research Protection, and requires information sharing with institutions of higher education related to foreign threats."
